 \"just the power\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s given me life back a little\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really kind of given me a fresh perspective on track and field.\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"a little\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"a fresh perspective\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve re-fallen in love with the sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d At 17, Wallace thought he knew exactly what the next few years of his life would hold.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3171, \"end\": 3178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few years\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born and raised in Athens, Ga., he had a track scholarship to the University of Georgia, the institution that anchored his hometown.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3278, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\", \"score\": 0.9999999141209664, \"rank\": 8.568430660572918e-08, \"text\": \"Ga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Year\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athens\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"a track scholarship\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"Georgia\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"the institution\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"his hometown\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His parents had met on campus as athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094tennis for him and track for her\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d never left.\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His parents\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"campus\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094tennis\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"her\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His father, Jeff, had gone on to become the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tennis coach, and Wallace grew up with the campus as his playground.\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3560, \"end\": 3567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His father\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"Jeff\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s tennis coach\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3554}, {\"ngram\": \"the campus\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"his playground\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He dreamed of eventually competing beyond college, perhaps even working toward the Olympics, but he knew that he wanted it all to start with running at UGA.\\u00c2 He never got the chance.\\u00c2 A nagging pain in his right leg was originally labeled a stress reaction.\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3660}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3794}, {\"ngram\": \"A nagging pain\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3809}, {\"ngram\": \"his right leg\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"a stress reaction\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it refused to go away, Wallace saw additional doctors and received a diagnosis of compartment syndrome.\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3899, \"end\": 3906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"additional doctors\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"a diagnosis\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"compartment syndrome\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The condition involves a painful buildup of pressure around the muscles and is not exceptionally unusual among runners: Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mother, Sabina, had experienced it herself in her running days.\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4120, \"end\": 4126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Sabina\", \"score\": 0.8695567568493374, \"rank\": 0.14999517546943752, \"text\": \"Sabina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Sabina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karel_Sabina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The condition\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3993}, {\"ngram\": \"a painful buildup\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4020}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4032}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s mother\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"her running days\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The surgery to treat compartment syndrome is typically straightforward.\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The surgery\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4187}, {\"ngram\": \"compartment syndrome\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace was told he could plan to begin training again soon after the procedure and expect to defend his state titles a few months later.\\u00c2 But there were complications with the procedure, leading to another surgery days later, leading to another which led to another which led to another.\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4248, \"end\": 4255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the procedure\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"his state titles\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4365}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 4385, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"complications\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4415}, {\"ngram\": \"the procedure\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4434}, {\"ngram\": \"another surgery\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4493}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4507, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, roughly 60% of his calf muscle was dead.\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"roughly 60%\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4561}, {\"ngram\": \"his calf muscle\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next two years were a mess of blood transfusions and skin grafts and pain.\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next two years\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4609}, {\"ngram\": \"a mess\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4621}, {\"ngram\": \"blood transfusions\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4643}, {\"ngram\": \"skin grafts\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4659}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace had 10 reconstructive surgeries in all.\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4670, \"end\": 4677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 reconstructive surgeries\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UGA honored his scholarship.\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4718, \"end\": 4721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.999871619951174, \"rank\": 0.00012839653236733218, \"text\": \"UGA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his scholarship\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was clear that he would not be able to run\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094certainly not competitively, and maybe not at all, in any capacity, ever again.\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any capacity\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vision Wallace had previously had for his immediate future disappeared.\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4890, \"end\": 4897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vision\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"his immediate future\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had no idea what might take its place.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was going from,I know what the next five, six years of my life are going to be, and they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re going to be the best,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cto literally needing care 24/7 and being in excruciating pain and addicted to pain medication and just trying to figure out what the rest of my life was going to be like.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t known what to think when a doctor first mentioned the possibility of amputation.\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 5408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5311, \"end\": 5318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"its place\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 4995}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"the next five, six years\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5055}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5066}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cto\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5160}, {\"ngram\": \"excruciating pain\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"pain medication\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5228}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 5264, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5283}, {\"ngram\": \"a doctor\", \"from\": 5351, \"to\": 5359}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"amputation\", \"from\": 5395, \"to\": 5405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d spent years undergoing painful reconstructive surgeries aimed specifically atsavinghis leg.\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5415}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5427}, {\"ngram\": \"painful reconstructive surgeries\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5471}, {\"ngram\": \"specifically atsavinghis leg\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would represent a total reversal of course.\", \"from\": 5508, \"to\": 5556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a total reversal\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5545}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he came to a point where amputation seemed like gaining something rather than losing it.\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5579}, {\"ngram\": \"amputation\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5596}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5617, \"to\": 5626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI saw it as an opportunity for a second chance,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace says.\", \"from\": 5650, \"to\": 5717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5704, \"end\": 5711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5679}, {\"ngram\": \"a second chance\", \"from\": 5684, \"to\": 5699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cInstead of loss\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the loss of self\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094it was an opportunity for hope and a way to get a second chance at life.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He made the call.\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cInstead\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"loss\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the loss\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5747}, {\"ngram\": \"self\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094it\", \"from\": 5751, \"to\": 5760}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 5765, \"to\": 5779}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5788}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 5793, \"to\": 5798}, {\"ngram\": \"a second chance\", \"from\": 5806, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"life.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few weeks after his 20th birthday, Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s right leg was amputated from the knee down.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 It was his eleventh surgery in less than three years.\", \"from\": 5852, \"to\": 6002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his 20th birthday\", \"from\": 5870, \"to\": 5887}, {\"ngram\": \"right leg\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"the knee\", \"from\": 5930, \"to\": 5938}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 5944, \"to\": 5947}, {\"ngram\": \"his eleventh surgery\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5975}, {\"ngram\": \"less than three years\", \"from\": 5979, \"to\": 6000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace and his parents had by then developed a routine: They would join him in the pre-op room with a Bible and pray together before he was wheeled away.\", \"from\": 6003, \"to\": 6157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6003, \"end\": 6010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his parents\", \"from\": 6015, \"to\": 6026}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6058}, {\"ngram\": \"the pre-op room\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6098}, {\"ngram\": \"a Bible\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet it felt different this time.\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace recognized that his parents were scared.\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6191, \"end\": 6198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his parents\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this surgery was one he was coming to by choice,hischoice, and he suddenly realized that he felt completely secure.\", \"from\": 6240, \"to\": 6359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this surgery\", \"from\": 6244, \"to\": 6256}, {\"ngram\": \"choice\", \"from\": 6285, \"to\": 6291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere was a fear that I saw in my parents\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 eyes, and I think it was the same fear they saw in my eyes for the first 10 surgeries,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace says.\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6499, \"end\": 6506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThere\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6369}, {\"ngram\": \"a fear\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6380}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 eyes\", \"from\": 6395, \"to\": 6413}, {\"ngram\": \"the same fear\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6447}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyes\", \"from\": 6460, \"to\": 6467}, {\"ngram\": \"the first 10 surgeries\", \"from\": 6472, \"to\": 6494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut for the first time, I had peace.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t choose amputation for a chance to run again.\", \"from\": 6513, \"to\": 6613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6538}, {\"ngram\": \"amputation\", \"from\": 6575, \"to\": 6585}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 6590, \"to\": 6598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If his initial reconstructive surgeries had been geared toward returning to the track, this one was in service of a larger, simpler goal.\", \"from\": 6614, \"to\": 6751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his initial reconstructive surgeries\", \"from\": 6617, \"to\": 6653}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 6690, \"to\": 6699}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 6701, \"to\": 6709}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6724}, {\"ngram\": \"a larger, simpler goal\", \"from\": 6728, \"to\": 6750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI just wanted to be pain-free,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace says.\", \"from\": 6752, \"to\": 6802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6789, \"end\": 6796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI just wanted to live a normal life.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d known that running prosthetics were an option and that, potentially, the surgery would mean he could finally get back to athletics.\\u00c2 Three months to the day after the amputation, Wallace tried a running prosthetic for the first time.What do I do?he asked his physical therapists, unsure of how different this would be from the running that he remembered, how many accommodations he would have to make.\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 7259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7037, \"end\": 7044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6807}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal life.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 6828, \"to\": 6845}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 6850, \"to\": 6856}, {\"ngram\": \"running prosthetics\", \"from\": 6868, \"to\": 6887}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 6893, \"to\": 6902}, {\"ngram\": \"the surgery\", \"from\": 6926, \"to\": 6937}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 6978, \"to\": 6987}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6988, \"to\": 6989}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 7006, \"to\": 7013}, {\"ngram\": \"the amputation\", \"from\": 7020, \"to\": 7034}, {\"ngram\": \"a running prosthetic\", \"from\": 7050, \"to\": 7070}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 7075, \"to\": 7089}, {\"ngram\": \"his physical therapists\", \"from\": 7112, \"to\": 7135}, {\"ngram\": \"unsure\", \"from\": 7137, \"to\": 7143}, {\"ngram\": \"the running\", \"from\": 7180, \"to\": 7191}, {\"ngram\": \"how many accommodations\", \"from\": 7212, \"to\": 7235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their answer surprised him:Just run.\", \"from\": 7260, \"to\": 7296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their answer\", \"from\": 7260, \"to\": 7272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The motions would be a little different, yes, but he could figure it out.\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The motions\", \"from\": 7297, \"to\": 7308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would still be running, the same as he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d loved all his life, what he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been missing and chasing and mourning for the last few years.\", \"from\": 7371, \"to\": 7512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 7412, \"to\": 7418}, {\"ngram\": \"all his life\", \"from\": 7425, \"to\": 7437}, {\"ngram\": \"what he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 7439, \"to\": 7450}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 7493, \"to\": 7511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Wallace had to do was start.\", \"from\": 7513, \"to\": 7545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7517, \"end\": 7524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He took off down the track.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 A year later, Wallace set a world record in the 100 meters at the 2011 Parapan American Games, and months after that, he was at the Paralympics in London.\", \"from\": 7546, \"to\": 7732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7592, \"end\": 7599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}, {\"begin\": 7725, \"end\": 7731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1538159226242224e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 7563, \"to\": 7572}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7576}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 7603, \"to\": 7617}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 7621, \"to\": 7635}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2011 Parapan American Games\", \"from\": 7639, \"to\": 7670}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 7705, \"to\": 7720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next decade brought success, personal and professional alike.\", \"from\": 7734, \"to\": 7799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next decade\", \"from\": 7734, \"to\": 7749}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 7758, \"to\": 7765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"London was followed by the Rio and Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 7800, \"to\": 7847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7800, \"end\": 7806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1538159226242224e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 7827, \"end\": 7830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.905930650023712, \"rank\": 0.10383725285552545, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 7835, \"to\": 7846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace won a combined three gold medals at the World Para Athletics Championships (twice in the 200 meters and once in the 100 meter relay) plus a bronze at the Paralympics in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 7848, \"to\": 8031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7848, \"end\": 7855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}, {\"begin\": 7896, \"end\": 7930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.697946074820969e-17, \"text\": \"World Para Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 8025, \"end\": 8030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6891758692862909, \"rank\": 0.45100834540102186, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a combined three gold medals\", \"from\": 7860, \"to\": 7888}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 meters\", \"from\": 7941, \"to\": 7955}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 meter relay\", \"from\": 7968, \"to\": 7987}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 8006, \"to\": 8021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside running, he started a foundation to help fellow amputees, and he met the woman who would become his wife, Lea.\", \"from\": 8032, \"to\": 8150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8146, \"end\": 8149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999780138753, \"rank\": 2.1986558210356763e-08, \"text\": \"Lea\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a foundation\", \"from\": 8060, \"to\": 8072}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow amputees\", \"from\": 8081, \"to\": 8096}, {\"ngram\": \"the woman\", \"from\": 8109, \"to\": 8118}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 8136, \"to\": 8144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They made a home together just outside Athens and had two sons.\", \"from\": 8151, \"to\": 8214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8190, \"end\": 8196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.7181091446650356, \"rank\": 0.39254577720936484, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a home\", \"from\": 8161, \"to\": 8167}, {\"ngram\": \"two sons\", \"from\": 8205, \"to\": 8213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as Wallace looked toward what seemed like his final Paralympic Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Paris at the age of 34\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094he wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t sure exactly what he wanted from them.\", \"from\": 8216, \"to\": 8366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8223, \"end\": 8230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his final Paralympic Games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Paris\", \"from\": 8262, \"to\": 8296}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 8300, \"to\": 8307}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 8333, \"to\": 8345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been sprinting for years.\", \"from\": 8368, \"to\": 8400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 8368, \"to\": 8374}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 8394, \"to\": 8399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training was beginning to feel rote.\", \"from\": 8401, \"to\": 8437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Training\", \"from\": 8401, \"to\": 8409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The events no longer sparked much in him.\", \"from\": 8438, \"to\": 8479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The events\", \"from\": 8438, \"to\": 8448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace knew, in theory, he wanted to keep going: In 2021, the stands had been empty due to the pandemic.\", \"from\": 8480, \"to\": 8585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8480, \"end\": 8487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theory\", \"from\": 8497, \"to\": 8503}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 8539, \"to\": 8549}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 8572, \"to\": 8584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted a chance to experience that same medal moment in front of a crowd, to hold his sons in his arms right afterwards.\", \"from\": 8586, \"to\": 8709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 8596, \"to\": 8604}, {\"ngram\": \"that same medal moment\", \"from\": 8619, \"to\": 8641}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 8645, \"to\": 8650}, {\"ngram\": \"a crowd\", \"from\": 8654, \"to\": 8661}, {\"ngram\": \"his sons\", \"from\": 8671, \"to\": 8679}, {\"ngram\": \"his arms\", \"from\": 8683, \"to\": 8691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that would mean committing to years of additional training at a point when he was beginning to feel sapped, and matters were complicated by a series of minor, nagging injuries.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 \\u00c2 Wallace began working with a new coach.\", \"from\": 8710, \"to\": 8936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8897, \"end\": 8904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 8744, \"to\": 8749}, {\"ngram\": \"additional training\", \"from\": 8753, \"to\": 8772}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 8776, \"to\": 8783}, {\"ngram\": \"matters\", \"from\": 8826, \"to\": 8833}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 8854, \"to\": 8862}, {\"ngram\": \"nagging injuries\", \"from\": 8873, \"to\": 8889}, {\"ngram\": \"a new coach\", \"from\": 8923, \"to\": 8934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Pfaff was a legend in the sport who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d coached dozens of Olympians and Paralympians.\", \"from\": 8937, \"to\": 9026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8937, \"end\": 8946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dan Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legend\", \"from\": 8951, \"to\": 8959}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 8963, \"to\": 8972}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 8989, \"to\": 8995}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 8999, \"to\": 9008}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympians\", \"from\": 9013, \"to\": 9025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now in semi-retirement, he specialized in helping athletes return from injury, but as they tried to figure out an issue with Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Achilles, the veteran coach spotted a different problem.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWatching some practices and some videos, going back and forth, you could just tell he wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t really motivated,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Pfaff says.\", \"from\": 9027, \"to\": 9353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9164, \"end\": 9172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1524840403716684e-14, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}, {\"begin\": 9342, \"end\": 9347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 9039, \"to\": 9049}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 9077, \"to\": 9085}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 9098, \"to\": 9104}, {\"ngram\": \"an issue\", \"from\": 9138, \"to\": 9146}, {\"ngram\": \"the veteran coach\", \"from\": 9174, \"to\": 9191}, {\"ngram\": \"a different problem\", \"from\": 9200, \"to\": 9219}, {\"ngram\": \"some practices\", \"from\": 9234, \"to\": 9248}, {\"ngram\": \"some videos\", \"from\": 9253, \"to\": 9264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been on a long grind.\", \"from\": 9354, \"to\": 9385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long grind\", \"from\": 9372, \"to\": 9384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could just tell the energy wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t there.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Pfaff thought on it and came back with a suggestion for Wallace: How do you feel about a new event at the age of 32?\\u00c2 There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s plenty of overlap between the skills needed for sprinting and long jump.\", \"from\": 9386, \"to\": 9638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9437, \"end\": 9442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}, {\"begin\": 9493, \"end\": 9500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 9406, \"to\": 9416}, {\"ngram\": \"wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 9417, \"to\": 9425}, {\"ngram\": \"a suggestion\", \"from\": 9475, \"to\": 9487}, {\"ngram\": \"a new event\", \"from\": 9523, \"to\": 9534}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 9538, \"to\": 9545}, {\"ngram\": \"32?\\u00c2\", \"from\": 9549, \"to\": 9553}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 9564, \"to\": 9570}, {\"ngram\": \"overlap\", \"from\": 9574, \"to\": 9581}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 9590, \"to\": 9600}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinting\", \"from\": 9612, \"to\": 9621}, {\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 9626, \"to\": 9635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But most athletes who do both start doing so in high school\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094they don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t convert without any prior experience in the twilight of their careers.\", \"from\": 9639, \"to\": 9784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most athletes\", \"from\": 9643, \"to\": 9656}, {\"ngram\": \"any prior experience\", \"from\": 9730, \"to\": 9750}, {\"ngram\": \"the twilight\", \"from\": 9754, \"to\": 9766}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 9770, \"to\": 9783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Pfaff suspected that long jump would be an especially good fit for Wallace.\", \"from\": 9785, \"to\": 9867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9792, \"end\": 9797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}, {\"begin\": 9859, \"end\": 9866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 9813, \"to\": 9822}, {\"ngram\": \"an especially good fit\", \"from\": 9832, \"to\": 9854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was his raw speed, yes, but also his elasticity with his left leg and his control of the running blade with his right.\", \"from\": 9868, \"to\": 9992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his raw speed\", \"from\": 9878, \"to\": 9891}, {\"ngram\": \"his elasticity\", \"from\": 9907, \"to\": 9921}, {\"ngram\": \"his left leg\", \"from\": 9927, \"to\": 9939}, {\"ngram\": \"his control\", \"from\": 9944, \"to\": 9955}, {\"ngram\": \"the running blade\", \"from\": 9959, \"to\": 9976}, {\"ngram\": \"his right\", \"from\": 9982, \"to\": 9991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as important as those physical qualities were his mental ones.\", \"from\": 9993, \"to\": 10060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those physical qualities\", \"from\": 10014, \"to\": 10038}, {\"ngram\": \"his mental ones\", \"from\": 10044, \"to\": 10059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s an attention-to-detail guy,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Pfaff says.\", \"from\": 10062, \"to\": 10114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10103, \"end\": 10108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"detail\", \"from\": 10088, \"to\": 10094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a process guy, whether he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s here or in business with his foundation or in his church\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s very intelligent, both academically but also athletically, and so if he understands the puzzle, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s pretty easy for him to make progression.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Pfaff began laying out the basics of the event, what needed to happen in each phase of the run, the takeoff, the jump.\", \"from\": 10115, \"to\": 10492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10374, \"end\": 10379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10122, \"to\": 10128}, {\"ngram\": \"a process guy\", \"from\": 10129, \"to\": 10142}, {\"ngram\": \"whether he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10144, \"to\": 10158}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 10170, \"to\": 10178}, {\"ngram\": \"his foundation\", \"from\": 10184, \"to\": 10198}, {\"ngram\": \"his church\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\", \"from\": 10205, \"to\": 10218}, {\"ngram\": \"the puzzle\", \"from\": 10310, \"to\": 10320}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10322, \"to\": 10328}, {\"ngram\": \"the basics\", \"from\": 10396, \"to\": 10406}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 10410, \"to\": 10419}, {\"ngram\": \"each phase\", \"from\": 10446, \"to\": 10456}, {\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 10460, \"to\": 10467}, {\"ngram\": \"the jump\", \"from\": 10482, \"to\": 10490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was an equation they could solve together.\", \"from\": 10493, \"to\": 10540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an equation\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace decided that experience might be exactly what he needed.\", \"from\": 10541, \"to\": 10605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10541, \"end\": 10548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 10562, \"to\": 10572}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 10582, \"to\": 10594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been sprinting for so long, he kind of just lost his love for it,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s wife, Lea.\", \"from\": 10607, \"to\": 10721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10717, \"end\": 10720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999780138753, \"rank\": 2.1986558210356763e-08, \"text\": \"Lea\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 10618, \"to\": 10624}, {\"ngram\": \"his love\", \"from\": 10674, \"to\": 10682}, {\"ngram\": \"Wallace\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s wife\", \"from\": 10699, \"to\": 10715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really cool to watch him love what he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s doing again.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 The new event came with all sorts of challenges.\", \"from\": 10722, \"to\": 10840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10767, \"to\": 10773}, {\"ngram\": \"The new event\", \"from\": 10791, \"to\": 10804}, {\"ngram\": \"all sorts\", \"from\": 10815, \"to\": 10824}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 10828, \"to\": 10838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(One that is minor but nonetheless annoying: Wallace has learned the long jump involves so much sand, everywhere, all the time.)\", \"from\": 10841, \"to\": 10969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10886, \"end\": 10893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 10906, \"to\": 10919}, {\"ngram\": \"so much sand\", \"from\": 10929, \"to\": 10941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But trying something new was invigorating, and beyond that, it helped reshape his mindset about what could be the final stretch of his athletic career.\", \"from\": 10970, \"to\": 11121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 10981, \"to\": 10990}, {\"ngram\": \"his mindset\", \"from\": 11048, \"to\": 11059}, {\"ngram\": \"the final stretch\", \"from\": 11080, \"to\": 11097}, {\"ngram\": \"his athletic career\", \"from\": 11101, \"to\": 11120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Failure seemed less damning.\", \"from\": 11122, \"to\": 11150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Failure\", \"from\": 11122, \"to\": 11129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trying to exercise control over every little thing felt less important.\", \"from\": 11151, \"to\": 11222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 11170, \"to\": 11177}, {\"ngram\": \"every little thing\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d found a new challenge in the long jump, but he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d found an unexpected freedom, too.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTransitioning to a new event\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 It was like, hey, yeah, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to mess up a lot.\", \"from\": 11223, \"to\": 11405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 11223, \"to\": 11229}, {\"ngram\": \"a new challenge\", \"from\": 11236, \"to\": 11251}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 11255, \"to\": 11268}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 11274, \"to\": 11280}, {\"ngram\": \"an unexpected freedom\", \"from\": 11287, \"to\": 11308}, {\"ngram\": \"a new event\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\", \"from\": 11336, \"to\": 11350}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 11375, \"to\": 11380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lot I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve got to learn,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace says.\", \"from\": 11406, \"to\": 11459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11446, \"end\": 11453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 11416, \"to\": 11421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut every time I fail, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to teach me something that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to help me get closer to where I want to be.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 That process has involved trying out new running blades and tinkering with mechanics and, of course, trying to nail the landing on that narrow board for take-off.\", \"from\": 11460, \"to\": 11748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 11486, \"to\": 11492}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 11511, \"to\": 11520}, {\"ngram\": \"That process\", \"from\": 11585, \"to\": 11597}, {\"ngram\": \"new running blades\", \"from\": 11622, \"to\": 11640}, {\"ngram\": \"mechanics\", \"from\": 11660, \"to\": 11669}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 11678, \"to\": 11684}, {\"ngram\": \"the landing\", \"from\": 11701, \"to\": 11712}, {\"ngram\": \"that narrow board\", \"from\": 11716, \"to\": 11733}, {\"ngram\": \"take-off\", \"from\": 11738, \"to\": 11746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re hitting a board that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 20 centimeters wide, it has to be perfect,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Wallace says.)\", \"from\": 11749, \"to\": 11852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11838, \"end\": 11845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.876721169437029