ace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second life\", \"from\": 12014, \"to\": 12027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he found a turning point when he competed in both disciplines at the 2023 U.S. Paralympics Championships.\", \"from\": 12099, \"to\": 12208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a turning point\", \"from\": 12112, \"to\": 12127}, {\"ngram\": \"both disciplines\", \"from\": 12148, \"to\": 12164}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 U.S. Paralympics Championships\", \"from\": 12168, \"to\": 12207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wallace took gold in the 100 meters and bronze in the long jump.\", \"from\": 12209, \"to\": 12273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12209, \"end\": 12216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"score\": 0.999961234290989, \"rank\": 3.8767211694370296e-05, \"text\": \"Wallace\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alfred_Russel_Wallace\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 12222, \"to\": 12226}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 12230, \"to\": 12244}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 12249, \"to\": 12255}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 12259, \"to\": 12272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet when he sat down for his debrief with Pfaff, he was clearly more excited to discuss the latter, starting with just how muchfunhe felt in the long jump.\", \"from\": 12274, \"to\": 12429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12316, \"end\": 12321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his debrief\", \"from\": 12299, \"to\": 12310}, {\"ngram\": \"muchfunhe\", \"from\": 12397, \"to\": 12406}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 12415, \"to\": 12428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pfaff figured that said enough.\", \"from\": 12430, \"to\": 12461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12430, \"end\": 12435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1632566822141545e-13, \"text\": \"Pfaff\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfaff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This gold seemed like a perfect close to his career in the 100, going out on top as the national champion, and this bronze felt like a perfect opening to dedicating himself entirely to long jump.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI can see a new brightness in him towards his craft that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really refreshing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Lea says.\", \"from\": 12462, \"to\": 12755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12746, \"end\": 12749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999780138753, \"rank\": 2.1986558210356763e-08, \"text\": \"Lea\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lea_Salonga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This gold\", \"from\": 12462, \"to\": 12471}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 12503, \"to\": 12513}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 12539, \"to\": 12542}, {\"ngram\": \"the national champion\", \"from\": 12546, \"to\": 12567}, {\"ngram\": \"this bronze\", \"from\": 12573, \"to\": 12584}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect opening\", \"from\": 12595, \"to\": 12612}, {\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 12647, \"to\": 12656}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 12657, \"to\": 12663}, {\"ngram\": \"a new brightness\", \"from\": 12672, \"to\": 12688}, {\"ngram\": \"his craft\", \"from\": 12704, \"to\": 12713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEspecially now going into the Game